  "2378230": {
    "name": "Neo Junk City",
    "steam_appid": 2378230,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/3e56d4afbbea20def514963c32b62d1c.apng?t=1769756269\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/3e56d4afbbea20def514963c32b62d1c.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" class=\"bb_img\" width=642 height=228 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 Neo Junk City</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里，霓虹灯光永不熄灭，城市的阴暗角落却暗流涌动。故事发生在反乌托邦的“沉没之城（Drowned City）”，这款沉浸式赛博朋克冒险游戏为传统的“点击解谜（point-and-click）”类型注入全新活力。你将置身于半淹没的都市中，调查谋杀案、在危机四伏的街头飞驰、并一路杀出重围，对抗成群的机器人、疯子以及赛博改造的怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/d2951cac885a11d6005c976fc4a3cb22.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" width=800 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/d2951cac885a11d6005c976fc4a3cb22.webm?t=1769756269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>引人入胜的剧情</strong><br>你将扮演 Buster 09，穿梭于沉没之城，揭开一起谋杀案的真相。唯一的问题在于：你知道凶手就是你自己，但却不记得你为何这么做。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态交互系统</strong><br>利用情境感知的“交互模块”，它们会根据你的探索程度和与角色的关系不断演变，为传统点击式解谜玩法带来全新的互动方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>街机风格竞速关卡</strong><br>在霓虹闪耀的街头体验高速追逐，将经典街机赛车元素与冒险要素相融合，带来紧张刺激的竞速体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紧凑刺激的射击动作</strong><br>你需要在瞬息万变的场景中考验反应速度与准度。敌人会突然出现，唯有最快的射击手才能生存下来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>华丽像素艺术</strong><br>细腻的像素风格将赛博朋克世界的魅力表现得淋漓尽致，让你仿佛置身于这座充满霓虹与危机的城市之中。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不断变化的游戏世界</strong><br>随着故事的推进，你对社区的影响将引起世界的改变，塑造出一个真正具有生命力的沉没之城。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好踏上一场充满危险与奇幻的旅程了吗？Neo Junk City 的大门已经为你敞开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/30b723e76ad5bc856277c2e82997264b.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" width=800 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/30b723e76ad5bc856277c2e82997264b.webm?t=1769756269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>调查</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过动态交互图标与周围世界深度互动。随着你探索各种物品，并与形形色色的市民建立联系，这些图标也会随之进化。挖掘隐藏的互动方式，解锁全新道路，并与这座城市中的多样角色建立新的羁绊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/f002f866989a64185b5fc8ecca6fcebe.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" width=800 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/f002f866989a64185b5fc8ecca6fcebe.webm?t=1769756269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驾驶</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Neo Junk City，绝不仅仅是侦探工作这么简单！在霓虹闪耀的街头体验快节奏、复古风格的赛车关卡，宛如重返经典街机时代。时刻提防「高速管理局」(Highway Authority System) 对道路的严苛监管——如果你开得太慢，他们不止会吊销你的驾照，甚至会剥夺你的生存权利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/d1cbd5de14f1fb8450b726045d3285a7.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" width=800 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/d1cbd5de14f1fb8450b726045d3285a7.webm?t=1769756269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>射击</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入刺激的高风险枪战，在电光火石的瞬间做出决定，凭借精准无比的枪法才能生存。应对突然出现的目标时，你必须识别威胁、分辨路人，并掌握最佳时机来击破敌人。每一场战斗都考验你的速度与准度，让你仿佛置身节奏紧凑的像素风格射击游戏，重温复古街机的热血快感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/c79917b9604dee60e9f28dd69d0910a0.poster.avif?t=1769756269\" width=800 height=319 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378230/extras/c79917b9604dee60e9f28dd69d0910a0.webm?t=1769756269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当水位不断上涨，你能拯救这座城市免于自我毁灭吗？踏上这段不可思议的旅程，探寻 Neo Junk City 中幽暗却又霓虹閃耀的夢境之旅吧！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 日语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 德语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文",
